SELECT  CONCAT(REPEAT(" ", $filled_size - CHAR_LENGTH(CAST(Abonnenten as STRING))), REPLACE(CAST(FORMAT("%'.0f", CAST(ROUND(Abonnenten) as NUMERIC)) AS STRING), ",", "."))FROM

  subscribers AS Abonnenten 
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtube`
WHERE profileId = $profileID 
AND time = (SELECT MAX(time) from ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtube WHERE profileId = $profileID and subscribers>0 and DATE(time) <= "$FollowersTimeRangeLastDay")
  AND subscribers > 0 
  )

SELECT
time as Datum,
CONCAT(
  CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)  END ,
  ":",CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)  END) as Dauer,
   title,
views,
link,
likes,
comments,
thumbnail,
CONCAT(REPLACE(CAST(ROUND(SAFE_DIVIDE((likes + comments),views)*100,1) AS STRING),".",","),"%") as interaction_rate
 FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtubeVideos` 
WHERE profileId = $profileID
AND $zeitraum
ORDER BY views DESC

SELECT
time as Datum,
CONCAT(
  CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)  END ,
  ":",CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)  END) as Dauer,
   title,
views,
CONCAT("Datum: ", FORMAT_TIMESTAMP('%d.%m.%y | %H:%M Uhr', DATETIME(time, 'Europe/Berlin')), " - ", "Videostarts: ",REPLACE(FORMAT("%'d", IFNULL(views,0)), ",", ".")) as formatted_views,
link,
likes,
comments,
thumbnail,
CONCAT(REPLACE(CAST(ROUND(SAFE_DIVIDE((likes + comments),views)*100,1) AS STRING),".",","),"%") as interaction_rate
 FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.youtubeVideos` 
WHERE profileId = $profileID
AND $zeitraum
ORDER BY views DESC

query.rawSql:
SELECT CASE a.LRA
WHEN "KiKa" THEN "KiKA"
ELSE a.LRA END
FROM (
  SELECT DISTINCT LRA FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles`
  WHERE youtubeID != 0
) as a
ORDER BY (
  CASE
    WHEN REGEXP_CONTAINS(LOWER("${__user.email}"), LOWER(a.LRA))
    THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END
) DESC

SELECT a.profile 
FROM 
(SELECT profile FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles` WHERE LRA = '$LRA_mapping' AND youtubeId != 0) as a,
(SELECT  Profil_YT FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.default-settings` WHERE LRA = '$LRA_mapping') as b
ORDER BY( 
CASE WHEN a.profile = b.Profil_YT THEN 1
ELSE 2
END
), UPPER(a.profile) ASC

    CASE WHEN (EXTRACT(HOUR from TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}')) = 23 AND EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}')) = 59 AND EXTRACT(SECOND FROM TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}')) = 59) THEN 
     CAST(date_diff(DATE('${__to:date:iso}'), DATE('${__from:date:iso}'), DAY) + 1 AS STRING)
    ELSE CAST(date_diff(DATE('${__to:date:iso}'), DATE('${__from:date:iso}'), DAY) AS STRING)
    END ;

query.rawSql:
SELECT CASE 

       --  case: "Last 24 HOURS "
    WHEN DATE('${__from:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin") >= CURRENT_DATE("Europe/Berlin")  OR TIMESTAMP_DIFF(TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}'), TIMESTAMP('${__from:date:iso}'), HOUR) = 24 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM DATETIME('${__from:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin")) != EXTRACT(DAY FROM DATETIME('${__to:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin")) OR TIMESTAMP_DIFF(TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}'), TIMESTAMP('${__from:date:iso}'), MINUTE) < 1439
    THEN """(EXTRACT(DATE from DATETIME(time, "Europe/Berlin"))  = DATE_ADD(CURRENT_DATE,INTERVAL 1 DAY))"""
    -- case: CURRENT_DATE()
    WHEN EXTRACT(DATE FROM TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}')) >= CURRENT_DATE("Europe/Berlin") 
    THEN  """(EXTRACT(DATE from DATETIME(time, "Europe/Berlin")) BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}', "Europe/Berlin") AND DATE_SUB("$HeuteDatum", INTERVAL 1 DAY))"""
    ELSE  """(EXTRACT(DATE from DATETIME(time, "Europe/Berlin")) BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}', "Europe/Berlin") AND DATE('${__to:date}', "Europe/Berlin"))"""

    END

SELECT CASE 
-- case: last x<24 hours
    WHEN TIMESTAMP_DIFF(TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}'), TIMESTAMP('${__from:date:iso}'), HOUR) = 24 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM DATETIME('${__from:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin")) != EXTRACT(DAY FROM DATETIME('${__to:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin")) OR TIMESTAMP_DIFF(TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}'), TIMESTAMP('${__from:date:iso}'), MINUTE) < 1439
    THEN   DATE_ADD(CURRENT_DATE,INTERVAL 1 DAY)
-- SECOND case: today or bigger
    WHEN EXTRACT(DATE FROM TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}')) >= CURRENT_DATE("Europe/Berlin") 
    THEN DATE_SUB("$HeuteDatum", INTERVAL 1 DAY)
ELSE DATE_SUB(DATE('${__to:date}', "Europe/Berlin"), INTERVAL 0 DAY)
END

SELECT CASE CONTAINS_SUBSTR("""${zeitraum}""", "DATE_ADD")
WHEN True  THEN "# Hinweis: FÃ¼r den ausgewÃ¤hlten Zeitraum liegen keine Daten vor. Um Daten auswerten zu kÃ¶nnen, bitte gestern oder grÃ¶Ãere ZeitrÃ¤ume auswÃ¤hlen."
ELSE """## Der ausgewertete Zeitraum lautet: $fromDay - $toDay """
END

SELECT CASE 
-- case: last x<24 hours
    WHEN TIMESTAMP_DIFF(TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}'), TIMESTAMP('${__from:date:iso}'), HOUR) = 24 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM DATETIME('${__from:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin")) != EXTRACT(DAY FROM DATETIME('${__to:date:iso}', "Europe/Berlin")) OR TIMESTAMP_DIFF(TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}'), TIMESTAMP('${__from:date:iso}'), MINUTE) < 1439
    THEN   FORMAT_DATE("%d.%m.%y",DATE_ADD(CURRENT_DATE,INTERVAL 1 DAY))
-- SECOND case: today or bigger
    WHEN EXTRACT(DATE FROM TIMESTAMP('${__to:date:iso}')) >= CURRENT_DATE("Europe/Berlin") 
    THEN FORMAT_DATE("%d.%m.%y",DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE("Europe/Berlin"), INTERVAL 1 DAY))
ELSE FORMAT_DATE("%d.%m.%y",DATE_SUB(DATE('${__to:date}', "Europe/Berlin"), INTERVAL 0 DAY))
END

WHEN "KiKA" THEN "KiKa"
ELSE "$LRA" END
